{{Italic title}}
'''''Beta. Scandinavian Journal of Business Research''''' is a biannual [[peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] covering research on [[management]] and business related themes and topics. The journal was established in 1987 and is published by [[Universitetsforlaget]]. Its [[editor-in-chief]] is Bjarne Espedal. Since 2006 the journal has been published online-only.

